	<td valign=top NOWRAP>$100,000</td>
	<td valign=top>Implement the Puerto Rico Energy Efficiency Code for Building Contruction that will set minimum requirements for the energy efficient design of new buildings, residential and non-residential buildings, so that they be constructed, operated and maintained in a manner that minimizes the use of energy without constraining the building function or the comfort level or productivity of the occupants.</td>
</tr>
	
</table>


