Charles Clinton<br />
District of Columbia Energy Office<br />
PH: (202) 673-6710<BR>


<P><B>Other Contact(s):</B><BR>

Sharon Cooke<br />
District of Columbia Energy Office<br />
PH: (202) 673-6738<BR>


<P><B>State website(s):</B><BR>


	Not Available<BR>


<P><B>Current Status Residential:</B><BR>
1995 MEC with 1999 DC supplements is mandatory.<BR>


<P><B>Can use MECcheck to show compliance:</B><BR>

