<h2>Iowa DOE Status of State Energy Codes</h2>
<br>
<B>Primary Technical Contact:</B><BR>


	Leo Duffy<BR>

	Facilities Engineer<BR>

	Iowa Fire Marshal's Office<BR>

	621 East 2nd Street<BR>

	Des Moines, 

	IA  
50319-1831<BR>

	PH:  (515) 281-5132  

	<BR>

	FX:  (515) 242-6299<BR>


<P><B>State Agency/Office Head:</B><BR>


	Not Available<BR>


