<h2>Missouri DOE Status of State Energy Codes</h2>
<br>
<B>Primary Technical Contact:</B><BR>


	Mike Bumgardner<BR>

	Department of Natural Resources, Energy Center<BR>

	Energy Technical Assistance Program<BR>

	P.O. Box 176<BR>

	1659 East Elm Street<BR>

