<h2>New York DOE Status of State Energy Codes</h2>
<br>
<B>Primary Technical Contact:</B><BR>


	Raymond J. Andrews, RA<BR>

	Assistant Director of Energy<BR>

	Codes Division<BR>

	NYS Department of State<BR>

	41 State Street<BR>

	Albany, 

	NY  
12231<BR>

	PH:  (518) 474-4073  

	<BR>

	FX:  (518) 486-4487<BR>


<P><B>State Agency/Office Head:</B><BR>

Randy A. Daniels, Secretary of State

<p>George E. Clark, Jr., Director<br />
Codes Division</p><BR>


