<h2>Virginia DOE Status of State Energy Codes</h2>
<br>
<B>Primary Technical Contact:</B><BR>


	George W. Rickman, Jr.<BR>

	Agency Regulatory Coordinator<BR>

	Division of Building and Fire Regulation<BR>

	VA Department of Housing and Community Development<BR>

	501 N. 2nd St.,  The Jackson Center<BR>

	Richmond, 

	VA  
23219-1321<BR>

	PH:  (804) 371-7180  

	<BR>

	FX:  (804) 371-7092<BR>


<P><B>State Agency/Office Head:</B><BR>

Jack A. Proctor<br />
Deputy Director<br />
PH: (804) 371-7150<BR>


