<P><B>State website(s):</B><BR>

West Virginia Energy Efficiency Program:  <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20020417130527/http://www.wvdo.org/community/eep.htm">http://www.wvdo.org/community/eep.htm</a><BR>


<P><B>Current Status Residential:</B><BR>
State building code based on ASHRAE 90A-1980 and 90B-1975, is adopted by local jurisdictions.<BR>


<P><B>Can use MECcheck to show compliance:</B><BR>

