<h2>Wisconsin DOE Status of State Energy Codes</h2>
<br>
<B>Primary Technical Contact:</B><BR>


	Randy Baldwin<BR>

	Bureau Director<BR>

	Wisconsin Department of Commerce<BR>

	Bureau of Integrated Srvcs, Div. of Safety & Bldgs<BR>

	P.O. Box 2658<BR>

	201 W. Washington Ave<BR>

	Madison, 

	WI  
53701-2658<BR>

	PH:  (608) 267-9152  

	<BR>

	FX:  (608) 267-9566<BR>


<P><B>State Agency/Office Head:</B><BR>

Mike Corry, Division Administrator<br />
Division of Safety and Buildings<br />
PH: (608) 266-1816<BR>


<P><B>Other Contact(s):</B><BR>

Randy Dahmen<br />
Commercial Building Code<br />
Division of Safety and Buildings<br />
PH: (608) 266-3162

<p>Berni Mattsson<br />
Code Development<br />
